<paragraph blockId="5.[178,1085,548,629]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1554">
Distribution and bionomics: ThetypelocalityissituatedinPhongsaly province in northern 
<collectingCountry box="[450,499,579,600]" name="Laos" pageId="5" pageNumber="1554">Laos</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation box="[515,584,578,600]" captionStart="Map 1" captionStartId="1.[178,223,1480,1500]" captionTargetBox="[178,1085,714,1470]" captionTargetId="figure-204@1.[178,1085,714,1470]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="Map 1: Distributions of Neosclerus macer nov.sp. (open circle) and N. barbatulus ASSING (filled and open circles) in South Asia." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5302502" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5302502/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="1554">Map 1</figureCitation>
